X-Build-Environment: This package wraps a pre-built FlagTree wheel into a .deb.
 The wheel is produced in a backend-specific container (see
 packaging/debian/build-helpers/Dockerfile.deb) which provides LLVM, CMake,
 Ninja and the chip vendor toolchain. The Build-Depends above are only what
 dpkg-buildpackage needs to assemble the .deb after the wheel is built.

Package: python3-flagtree-nvidia
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3:any,
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         python3-filelock,
